{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_RestoreSpecialPosition}}
'''A_RestoreSpecialPosition'''

(no parameters)
{{Warning|text=This function should not be used. This article is for the purposes of complete documentation only.}}

Puts the calling actor back to its spawning position. This, along with [[A_RestoreSpecialDoomThing]] or [[A_RestoreSpecialThing1]] and [[A_RestoreSpecialThing2]], is used by the engine to "respawn" pickup items that were "hidden" after pickup.

[[category:Decorate Internal functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:RestoreSpecialPosition}}
